name: DDRECORD_001
description: Highspeed inmate scanner, the records of 249 dosed dudes. An investment? A gold mine! Privacy of the individuals is kept sacrosanct with their metadata hidden and only their faces visible, very, very, very briefly. It gives you a real feel for the population and what you might be able to do to them! This is a record of the dudes and not the dudes themselves. YOU ARE NOT CONFINING 249 DOSED DUDES TO ONE BLOCK THAT IS INHUMANE. Think of this as flicking through the yellow pages of dosed dudes, have a look, see what you like? Keep an eye out as we may need to sell them off to a private block and that could very well be yours! Dudes rock!
